column2: HOW DO I CHANGE OR UPDATE MY PERSONAL INFORMATION-    The New York Times Home Delivery Web Account. You may update and/or edit your Home Delivery account information online at the Home Delivery website by clicking on the link for Update Account. Should you require assistance, please call our toll free number, 1-800-NYTIMES.
Manage Your NYTimes.com Account in the My Account Area. You may review and update your NYTimes.com membership or account information and access your transaction history in the My Account area.
